    "placement_highlights": "Udayana University maintains a strong regional presence with a high concentration of graduates entering the tourism and financial sectors in Bali. The [Career Development Center](https://cdc.unud.ac.id/) actively hosts 'Udayana Career Days' and 'Inspire Career Week' to bridge the gap between fresh graduates and national enterprises. Recent [Tracer Study](https://feb.unud.ac.id/posts/tracer-study-student-satisfaction-evaluation-report-for-the-bachelor-of-accounting-study-program) reports indicate that over 70% of graduates secure employment or start businesses within six months of graduation."
